abstract: A Bruce Springsteen archive has outgrown the Asbury Park Public Library.
snippet: A Bruce Springsteen archive has outgrown the Asbury Park Public Library.
lead_paragraph: A collection of documents, articles and books about Bruce Springsteen's career that has been growing for years at the Asbury Park Public Library will be moved to nearby Monmouth University in West Long Branch, N.J., the university said.

headline.main: A Boss Collection for a New Jersey University
